Title: A La Cart
Plot: The CSI team investigates two unusual cases, one involving the suspicious death of a go-cart racer who took his hobby to the highway and paid the price with his life, and a murder at a hip new restaurant where patrons dine in the dark
ParentalRatingReason: R16 Violence and content that may disturb
